The paper deals with device-free localization (DFL) using transceivers, which is a topic related to networked systems and communication (cs.NI). The paper also mentions security situations, which could fall under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). The use of autonomous vehicles to deploy and move the transceivers could be considered a robotics application (cs.RO). The paper also mentions emergency situations, which could fall under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper mentions monitoring the daily activities of elderly or special needs individuals, which could fall under the category of physical education and sport (cs.PE).
